articles.title: Surfer attacked in Australia by suspected great white shark hospitalized, clinging to life - USA TODAY
articles.description: A surfer is in the hospital after suffering "life-threatening injuries" in a suspected great white shark attack off Australia’s east coast.
articles.content:
A surfer is in the hospital after suffering life-threatening injuries in a suspected great white shark attack off Australias east coast Friday, police said.
